        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 8 at 6:30PM CDT until June 8 at 6:45PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 630 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 8 miles southwest of
Channing, or 22 miles north of Vega, moving southeast at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.
People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles.

Locations impacted include...
Channing.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
